SE 2: SAFETY CHECK\\nFor EACH finding: \"Can this change produce different output for ANY input?\"\\nDROP if: merging functions, removing checks, changing error messages/exit codes/output format,\\nchanging operation order, changing defaults/signatures, changing data structures, not 100% certain, category E not trivially safe.\\n\\nPHASE 3: APPLY\\nApply ONLY APPROVED changes. One edit at a time. Re-read after. Revert if wrong. Max 30 edits per file.\\nA missed cleanup is acceptable. A broken test is not.\\n\\'']", "timestamp": "2026-06-04 23:14:43", "level": "verbose", "process_id": 3785304, "thread_name": "MainThread"}
